{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"5000000000000001","type":"group","x":-100,"y":80,"width":3200,"height":850,"label":"Seven single-authority workflows","color":"5"},
		{"id":"5000000000000002","type":"group","x":-100,"y":990,"width":3200,"height":680,"label":"Four cross-authority workflows","color":"6"},
		{"id":"5000000000000003","type":"group","x":3160,"y":80,"width":520,"height":1590,"label":"Entry, gates, and state separation","color":"1"},
		{"id":"6000000000000001","type":"text","x":-100,"y":-180,"width":3780,"height":180,"text":"# Career OS Workflow Guide Â· Start with an outcome\n\nSay what you want. The Agent selects Skills, reads canonical records, performs authorized local work, and verifies the result.","color":"5"},
		{"id":"6000000000000002","type":"text","x":-20,"y":160,"width":400,"height":500,"text":"## Single-domain 1 Â· Evidence\n\n- **Say:** â€śCapture this result and my exact contribution.â€ť\n- **Agent:** Preserve provenance, attribution, support, and uncertainty.\n- **Skills:** `career-evidence` Â· capture, debrief, consolidate\n- **Authority:** Career Evidence\n- **Result:** Traceable Capture, Work, Story, or Claim candidate.\n- **Gate:** Raw material never becomes an approved public Claim.\n- **Verify:** `career-os check`","color":"5"},
		{"id":"6000000000000003","type":"text","x":430,"y":160,"width":400,"height":500,"text":"## Single-domain 2 Â· Strategy\n\n- **Say:** â€śAlign my durable direction and next-year plan.â€ť\n- **Agent:** Compare repeated evidence, preferences, constraints, plans, and reviewed inputs.\n- **Skills:** `career-strategy` Â· position, plan, align\n- **Authority:** Career Strategy\n- **Result:** Positioning, Career Lane, or dated plan.\n- **Gate:** One JD, company, interview, or signal cannot rewrite Strategy.\n- **Verify:** `career-os check`","color":"5"},
		{"id":"6000000000000004","type":"text","x":880,"y":160,"width":400,"height":500,"text":"## Single-domain 3 Â· Role Market\n\n- **Say:** â€śPreserve and screen these JDs against my evidence.â€ť\n- **Agent:** Retain source fidelity; separate requirements, fit, gaps, and uncertainty.\n- **Skills:** `role-market` Â· discover, ingest, screen, compare, review\n- **Authority:** Role Market\n- **Result:** Direction or one dated JD Note with its screening judgment.\n- **Gate:** Screening stays inside the JD Note and never implies Company quality, readiness, or application.\n- **Verify:** `career-os check`","color":"5"},
		{"id":"6000000000000005","type":"text","x":1330,"y":160,"width":400,"height":500,"text":"## Single-domain 4 Â· Opportunity\n\n- **Say:** â€śResearch the company and track contact without marking an application.â€ť\n- **Agent:** Separate Company, Scope, Engagement, events, decision, and unknowns.\n- **Skills:** `opportunity-decision` Â· research, scope, track, decide\n- **Authority:** Opportunity Decision\n- **Result:** Sourced facts, bounded engagement, or dated decision.\n- **Gate:** Tracking never authorizes contact, application, upload, offer action, or resignation.\n- **Verify:** `career-os check`","color":"5"},
		{"id":"6000000000000006","type":"text","x":1780,"y":160,"width":400,"height":500,"text":"## Single-domain 5 Â· Outlook\n\n- **Say:** â€śReview this two-year thesis from current primary sources.â€ť\n- **Agent:** Preserve event dates, publication dates, freshness, scope, uncertainty, and invalidation.\n- **Skills:** `career-outlook` Â· scan, synthesize, review\n- **Authority:** Career Outlook\n- **Result:** Dated Signal, Thesis, or Review.\n- **Gate:** Pending research or one signal never changes Strategy.\n- **Verify:** `career-os check`","color":"5"},
		{"id":"6000000000000007","type":"text","x":2230,"y":160,"width":400,"height":500,"text":"## Single-domain 6 Â· Readiness\n\n- **Say:** â€śDiagnose this gap, teach it, then run a strict retest.â€ť\n- **Agent:** Anchor gaps, notes, sessions, criteria, reviewers, answers, and outcomes to a baseline.\n- **Skills:** `capability-readiness` Â· diagnose, learn, study-paper, practice, assess, retest\n- **Authority:** Capability Readiness\n- **Result:** Gap, Note, Session, or Assessment.\n- **Gate:** Learning and demos never become production evidence or formal readiness.\n- **Verify:** `career-os check`","color":"5"},
		{"id":"6000000000000008","type":"text","x":2680,"y":160,"width":400,"height":500,"text":"## Single-domain 7 Â· Communication\n\n- **Say:** â€śTailor this resume and create a safe preview.â€ť\n- **Agent:** Use only approved supported Claims; enforce audience, visibility, privacy, and export policy.\n- **Skills:** `career-communication` Â· compose, tailor, validate, export\n- **Authority:** Career Communication\n- **Result:** Profile, Resume, validation, or sanitized Export.\n- **Gate:** Public/application export needs explicit intent and never authorizes sending or upload.\n- **Verify:** `career-os resume export`","color":"5"},
		{"id":"7000000000000001","type":"text","x":-20,"y":710,"width":400,"height":140,"text":"## Career Evidence\n[[10-career-evidence.md|Open authority contract]]","color":"5"},
		{"id":"7000000000000002","type":"text","x":430,"y":710,"width":400,"height":140,"text":"## Career Strategy\n[[20-career-strategy.md|Open authority contract]]","color":"5"},
		{"id":"7000000000000003","type":"text","x":880,"y":710,"width":400,"height":140,"text":"## Role Market\n[[30-role-market.md|Open authority contract]]","color":"5"},
		{"id":"7000000000000004","type":"text","x":1330,"y":710,"width":400,"height":140,"text":"## Opportunity Decision\n[[40-opportunity-decision.md|Open authority contract]]","color":"5"},
		{"id":"7000000000000005","type":"text","x":1780,"y":710,"width":400,"height":140,"text":"## Career Outlook\n[[50-career-outlook.md|Open authority contract]]","color":"5"},
		{"id":"7000000000000006","type":"text","x":2230,"y":710,"width":400,"height":140,"text":"## Capability Readiness\n[[60-capability-readiness.md|Open authority contract]]","color":"5"},
		{"id":"7000000000000007","type":"text","x":2680,"y":710,"width":400,"height":140,"text":"## Career Communication\n[[70-career-communication.md|Open authority contract]]","color":"5"},
		{"id":"6000000000000009","type":"text","x":-20,"y":1070,"width":700,"height":440,"text":"## Cross-domain 1 Â· Current work â†’ Strategy\n\n- **Say:** â€śDoes my current work still reinforce my long-term direction?â€ť\n- **Agent:** Read current employment, attributable Work, active Strategy, reviewed Outlook, and Readiness constraints.\n- **Skills:** `opportunity-decision` + `career-evidence` + `career-strategy` Â· align\n- **Authority:** Employment facts â†’ Opportunity; completed work â†’ Evidence; plan â†’ Strategy\n- **Result:** Alignment judgment, plan update, or unresolved dependency.\n- **Gate:** Objectives are intent, not evidence; writes require explicit local update intent.\n- **Verify:** `career-os check`","color":"6"},
		{"id":"600000000000000a","type":"text","x":760,"y":1070,"width":700,"height":440,"text":"## Cross-domain 2 Â· Result â†’ Safe communication\n\n- **Say:** â€śTurn this result into supported audience-safe wording.â€ť\n- **Agent:** Preserve contribution and provenance, establish Claim support, then compose for the audience.\n- **Skills:** `career-evidence` + `career-communication`\n- **Authority:** Facts and Claims â†’ Evidence; wording and export â†’ Communication\n- **Result:** Traceable evidence, bounded wording, and optional safe preview.\n- **Gate:** Polish, raw Capture, plans, and unsupported metrics cannot cross the publication gate.\n- **Verify:** `career-os check` + `career-os resume export`","color":"6"},
		{"id":"600000000000000b","type":"text","x":1540,"y":1070,"width":700,"height":440,"text":"## Cross-domain 3 Â· JD â†’ Preparation â†’ Resume\n\n- **Say:** â€śScreen this role, research it, prepare real gaps, and tailor supported communication.â€ť\n- **Agent:** Keep JD screening, opportunity decision, application tracking, resume export, and interview readiness independent.\n- **Skills:** `role-market` + `opportunity-decision` + `capability-readiness` + `career-communication`\n- **Authority:** Each block writes only its owning records.\n- **Result:** Referenced fit, context, gaps, preparation, and target-specific artifact.\n- **Gate:** Learning cannot fill production evidence; no local result implies an application.\n- **Verify:** `career-os check --host` + export gate","color":"6"},
		{"id":"600000000000000c","type":"text","x":2320,"y":1070,"width":700,"height":440,"text":"## Cross-domain 4 Â· Outlook â†’ Strategy\n\n- **Say:** â€śShould reviewed external evidence change my direction or plan?â€ť\n- **Agent:** Compare reviewed Outlook with repeated personal and Role Market evidence, preferences, constraints, and plans.\n- **Skills:** `career-outlook` Â· review + `career-strategy` Â· position, plan, align\n- **Authority:** External thesis â†’ Outlook; accepted direction and plan â†’ Strategy\n- **Result:** Accept, reject, or defer with confidence and a review trigger.\n- **Gate:** One trend, JD, company, or pending thesis cannot rewrite a Career Lane.\n- **Verify:** `career-os check`","color":"6"},
		{"id":"7000000000000008","type":"text","x":-20,"y":1540,"width":700,"height":100,"text":"## Opportunity â†’ Evidence â†’ Strategy\n[[40-opportunity-decision.md|Opportunity]] Â· [[10-career-evidence.md|Evidence]] Â· [[20-career-strategy.md|Strategy]]","color":"6"},
		{"id":"7000000000000009","type":"text","x":760,"y":1540,"width":700,"height":100,"text":"## Evidence â†’ Communication\n[[10-career-evidence.md|Evidence]] Â· [[70-career-communication.md|Communication]]","color":"6"},
		{"id":"700000000000000a","type":"text","x":1540,"y":1540,"width":700,"height":100,"text":"## Market â†’ Opportunity â†’ Readiness â†’ Communication\n[[30-role-market.md|Market]] Â· [[40-opportunity-decision.md|Opportunity]] Â· [[60-capability-readiness.md|Readiness]] Â· [[70-career-communication.md|Communication]]","color":"6"},
		{"id":"700000000000000b","type":"text","x":2320,"y":1540,"width":700,"height":100,"text":"## Outlook â†’ Strategy\n[[50-career-outlook.md|Outlook]] Â· [[20-career-strategy.md|Strategy]]","color":"6"},
		{"id":"600000000000000d","type":"text","x":3220,"y":160,"width":400,"height":160,"text":"# Architecture overview\n[[career-map.canvas|Open the Agent-native map]]","color":"4"},
		{"id":"600000000000000e","type":"text","x":3220,"y":370,"width":400,"height":260,"text":"# Hard gates\n- External/account actions\n- Public or application-grade export\n- Irrecoverable overwrite or delete\n\nEach requires explicit intent.","color":"1"},
		{"id":"600000000000000f","type":"text","x":3220,"y":680,"width":400,"height":250,"text":"# State separation\nTool health â‰  evidence\nEvidence â‰  approved Claim\nClaim â‰  readiness\nReadiness â‰  application\nApplication â‰  outcome","color":"1"},
		{"id":"6000000000000010","type":"text","x":3220,"y":980,"width":400,"height":220,"text":"# Verification depth\n`check --fast` Â· structure\n`check` Â· records and semantics\n`check --host` Â· host references","color":"2"},
		{"id":"6000000000000011","type":"text","x":3220,"y":1250,"width":400,"height":340,"text":"# Five opportunity blocks\n1. JD screening\n2. Company decision\n3. Application tracking\n4. Resume tailoring/export\n5. Interview preparation/retest\n\nSuccess in one proves nothing about another.","color":"3"}
	],
